<br>
Myrln<br>
Erollisi Marr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utrobb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Trobb</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(8/18/01 12:23:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=18.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Wisps, Wisps and more Wisps</span><hr size=1> Doh!  Myrsila is at that location in North Karanas.  Just invis up and make that long run.  This is an awesome way to succeed as a mage and not have to be a twink <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
